des:
If you've ever wanted to learn more about Nicolas Cage, then this is the perfect Alexa skill for you! Expand your knowledge on the One True God today!

To get started say "Alexa ask Cage Facts to tell me a fact".

Try phrases such as these to get some great Nicolas Cage facts:
...tell me a fact
...tell me a Cage fact
...give me a fact
...give me a Cage fact
...give me trivia
...give me some information
...give me some Cage information
...tell me something
